These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-8-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, iced-tea
There 2 different types of food: raspberry, strawberry
House: cape-cod, modern
The people have 2 different jobs:  dancer, mechanic
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: drama, fantasy
There are 2 different nationalities: italian, thai
The people use 2 different means of transport: roller, tram
1. the mechanic is on the left or right of the person driving the roller##3
2. the person drinking iced-tea is not to the right of the dancer##8
3. the modern house is not the person watching drama movies##6
4. the modern house is somewhere to the left of the mechanic##5
5. the mechanic is not to the left of the person driving the roller##8
6. the thai is not the person driving the roller##6
7. the person eating raspberry is the cape-cod house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Beverage      | iced-tea   | coffee      |
| Food          | strawberry | raspberry   |
| House         | modern    | cape-cod |
| Job           | dancer     | mechanic    |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy    | drama       |
| Nationality   | italian    | thai        |
| Transport     | roller     | tram        |

